{
  "stem": "833.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "His and mother's support were there at all times.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I had no problem with my family being-- being a musician.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That problem came later on because of the question of space, because what-- what after-- what Vienna was after the war, after we lost the war, can-- cannot be imagined, how a city becomes devoid of any amenities.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was absolutely no food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was no food.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was nothing to heat with.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Most of the time, we didn't get electricity because there was no-- no way, no coal that they could fire the plants-- the plants.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a really desperate time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The reason why I'm still getting up",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "00 in the morning, at 4:30-- it's what I-- that's what I had to do.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Before school, I went around to every market in the neighborhood with my bicycle that had leather-- leather pneumatics--",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Tires-- leather tires, because rubber was-- was unavailable-- just to find out where I could get some of these ugly beets and things that you-- that you just fill your stomach with.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Let's say my winter coat, at that time-- I grew-- at that time, in 1918, I was full-- my full size.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was 6 foot 1 and 1/2.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, I've shrunk like Irish linen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I was really very tall, grew out of all my things.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So my winter coat was made out of paper.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You have a very-- it is impossible to imagine for any American what a city becomes when it loses, suddenly, every raison d'etre, practically.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This was the large capital of a-- of a large empire.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And suddenly, this empire was gone.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it was a small country of 7 million people who all tried to eke out a life for themselves.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
